tells a different story.

24
00:04:49,623 --> 00:04:51,291
A story about a jealous uncle

25
00:04:51,374 --> 00:04:53,960
whose attempts to usurp the throne
from the rightful king

26
00:04:54,044 --> 00:04:55,837
