214
00:16:02,962 --> 00:16:04,672
Now.

215
00:16:06,632 --> 00:16:08,217
(Breath quivering)

216
00:16:21,397 --> 00:16:24,567
The britches, too, reek. Take them off.

217
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:50,218
(Whimpering)

218
00:16:59,644 --> 00:17:01,354
(Water splashes)

219
00:17:26,462 --> 00:17:27,547
(Whimpers)

220
00:17:43,646 --> 00:17:44,772
(Gasps)

221
00:17:51,153 --> 00:17:53,489
Do you love me, reek?

222
00:17:59,870 --> 00:18:02,039
Yes, of course, my lord.

223
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,501
Good.

224
00:18:05,835 --> 00:18:09,922
